    <h1>The Crown<br><em>Restoration</em><br>Program</h1>
    <p class="hero-sub">Hair loss is not just a physical experience. It affects how you move through the world, how you see yourself, how you show up. This program exists to meet you where you are — with skill, sensitivity, and a plan.</p>
