<!-- UNDERSTANDING -->
<section class="understand-section reveal">
  <div>
    <p class="eyebrow">You Are Not Alone</p>
    <h2 class="section-title">Hair loss is<br>a <em>deeply personal</em><br>experience.</h2>
    <div class="rule"></div>
    <p class="body-text">Whether you're navigating traction alopecia from years of tight styles, or watching your hair thin in ways that feel out of your control — the emotional weight of it is real. The mirror tells a story you didn't choose. And finding someone who understands both the hair science and the human experience of hair loss is harder than it should be.</p>
    <p class="body-text">The Crown Restoration Program was created specifically for clients experiencing traction alopecia and general hair thinning. It is not a quick fix or a promise of results that no one can guarantee. It is a careful, individualized approach — one that protects what you have, works to support what may return, and gives you back something that hair loss often takes first: a sense of control.</p>
