      <h3 class="facing-card-title">General Thinning & Hair Loss</h3>
      <p class="facing-card-body">Thinning hair without a specific diagnosis — whether from hormonal shifts, nutritional deficiencies, stress, environmental factors, or simply the accumulation of years of less-than-ideal care. This program addresses general thinning with scalp health as the foundation, protective styling that reduces manipulation, and where appropriate, techniques designed to support regrowth conditions while keeping you feeling like yourself.</p>
